trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> class adds an entry to the directory.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> adiciona uma entrada para o diretório.

trans-unit.source: The request may be added to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument> or it can be used as the parameter for <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.SendRequest%2A>.
trans-unit.target: A solicitação pode ser adicionada para o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlRequestDocument> ou ele pode ser usado como o parâmetro <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.SendRequest%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> class.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" />.

trans-unit.source: The <c>distinguishedName</c> of the new object in the directory.
trans-unit.target: O <c>distinguishedName</c> do novo objeto no diretório.

trans-unit.source: An array, of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute" /> objects, that contains the attributes for this object.
trans-unit.target: Uma matriz, de objetos <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute" />, que contém os atributos para esse objeto.

trans-unit.source: This parameter may be <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Esse parâmetro pode ser <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute[])" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> class using the specified distinguished name and attributes.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttribute[])" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> usando o nome diferenciado e os atributos especificados.

trans-unit.source: The <c>distinguishedName</c> of the new object in the directory.
trans-unit.target: O <c>distinguishedName</c> do novo objeto no diretório.

trans-unit.source: The object class for this object.
trans-unit.target: A classe do objeto para esse objeto.

trans-unit.source: If this parameter is <see langword="null" />, an exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Se esse parâmetro for <see langword="null" />, uma exceção será lançada.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.String)" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> class using the specified <paramref name="distinguishedName" /> and the object class.
trans-unit.target: O construtor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.#ctor(System.String,System.String)" /> cria uma instância da classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest" /> usando o <paramref name="distinguishedName" /> e a classe de objeto especificados.

trans-unit.source: The value specified in the `objectClass` parameter is added to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.Attributes%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O valor especificado no `objectClass` parâmetro é adicionado para o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.Attributes%2A> propriedade.

trans-unit.source: This value can be modified after this constructor is called.
trans-unit.target: Esse valor pode ser modificado depois de chamar este construtor.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="objectClass" /> parameter contains a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: O parâmetro <paramref name="objectClass" /> é uma referência nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.Attributes" /> property contains a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttributeCollection" /> of attribute-value pairs for the object.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.Attributes" /> contém um <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttributeCollection" /> de pares de atributo/valor para o objeto.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttributeCollection" /> of attribute-value pairs for the object.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryAttributeCollection" /> de pares atributo-valor do objeto.

trans-unit.source: This property cannot be set.
trans-unit.target: Esta propriedade não pode ser definida.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.DistinguishedName" /> property contains the distinguished name of the object.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.DistinguishedName" /> contém o nome diferenciado do objeto.

trans-unit.source: The distinguished name of the object.
trans-unit.target: O nome distinto do objeto.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.ToXmlNode(System.Xml.XmlDocument)" /> method creates an XML node from the specified <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" /> object.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddRequest.ToXmlNode(System.Xml.XmlDocument)" /> cria um nó XML com base no objeto <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlDocument" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: The resulting <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" /> object.
trans-unit.target: O tipo do objeto <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlElement" /> resultante.
